    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This specimen represents a pinnacle of analog engineering, preserved in showroom condition. The naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six delivers a linear power band, benefiting from a dry-sump lubrication system and a high-flow intake manifold. The 6-speed manual transmission exhibits short, tactile throws with synchronized gate precision, feeding power through a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis features a multi-link rear suspension with monotube dampers, providing exceptional lateral stiffness and turn-in response. Brakes utilize cross-drilled rotors with four-piston monoblock calipers, showing zero thermal cycling or fade. Every bushing, seal, and fluid line remains factory-spec, ensuring a visceral, uncompromised driving experience for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
